It takes 4-5 seconds to insert the class name selected in the completion popup. Accordingly to the attached snapshot all the time is spent in ShortenReferences.process(KotlinClassifierInsertHandler.kt). The problem reproduces for Kotlin files in main_idea_tests module in IDEA Ultimate project, that module depends an almost all of other 700+ modules in IDEA Ultimate project. In other modules it works better.

Kotlin 1.1.1-release-IJ2017.1-1, IDEA 172.snapshot.